title: door
---
<<if $room == 1>>
    <<if has_item("key")>>
    Felix: I think I have the right item to open it.
    <<else>>
    Felix: It's locked.
    <<endif>>
<<elseif $room == 2>>
Felix: Maybe I should try another way out.
<<elseif $room == 3>>
    <<if $trydoor == 0>>
    Felix: 
    <<set $trydoor = 1>>
<<elseif $room == 4>>
Felix: 
<<elseif $room == 5>>
Felix: 
<<elseif $room == 6>>
Felix: 
<<else>>
Felix: I can't turn my back on this devil dog.
<<endif>>
===